UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'It\'s good to see another new arrival here at Forest Song.$B$BVindicator Palanaar is sending as much help as she can muster and each set of hands is appreciated.$B$BTake a look around, $C. It may not be much now, but with time and help from our night elf allies, we\'ll build a settlement worthy of calling home. There is much to be done here and any help you can provide would be welcome.' WHERE entry = 26453;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Have you slain Ran yet, my friend? We must have his skull if you\'re to deliver my people from bondage.', OfferRewardText = 'You have done well, my friend.$B$BNow quickly, hand me Ran\'s skull. While his essence yet taints it, we shall fashion it upon Dartol\'s Rod giving you the power to influence my brethren and deliver them from evil!' WHERE entry = 26481;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Do you think that you retrieved all of the troll charms from Thistlefur Hold?$B$BIf any are left behind, the Thistlefur tribe will continue to be influenced by them, and eventually they will attack this place.', OfferRewardText = '<Hephaestus nods slowly as he looks you straight in the eye.>$B$BYou\'ve likely saved the Thistlefur from themselves, at least in the short run.  If they can keep from stealing objects of power that don\'t belong to them, that is.$B$BI understand that the night elves are having problems with the other furbolg tribe to the south. That\'s something that Raene is going to want to speak to you about.$B$BHowever, there are more immediate concerns that I would ask for your help with. ' WHERE entry = 13874;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = '<The ancient creaks as it turns toward you.>$B$BArchitect Nemos said that you might be bringing wood salvaged from befouled Satyrnaar.', OfferRewardText = 'Wood warped by foul demonic magic is of no use to the draenei at Forest Song. Nothing sound can be built with it, but I shall purify it and return it in good time to Architect Nemos and his people for their use.$B$BSome good will come from this tragedy, after all.' WHERE entry = 26454;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'I\'d received a report about you from some of my scouts out in the forest but I had no idea how capable you are!$B$BThank you, $N. With what you\'ve accomplished the tide is turned. I\'ve no doubt now that we\'ll route them by the end of the day!' WHERE entry = 13624;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'At last we have sent a message that the orcs won\'t dare ignore. Any overseer or foreman who sets foot within the camp to replace Gorthak will feel my wrath!$B$BWe must press our advantage, $N, and never rest until the Warsong Lumber Camp is a distant memory and a glade of trees stands upon that ground.$B$BNow what was this about explosives...?' WHERE entry = 26457;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Fools!!$B$BThis Draaka woman has allowed herself to be manipulated by a demon!$B$B<Garrosh studies you for a moment.>$B$BAnd I smell its taint on you as well, $C.... ' WHERE entry = 13841;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = '$N, is that you? Have you returned with the cure for Relara?', OfferRewardText = 'Oh, $N, you have saved my daughter! I know the power of the moonstones will give back my daughter her strength!$B$BI can never repay you fully for the aid you have given me, but... please, take this. Other than Relara, it is my most dear possession.' WHERE entry = 13924;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Have you been successful in locating the fathom core?  Without it we\'ll have no idea what the Twilight\'s Hammer is exactly up to down there.', OfferRewardText = 'This is exactly what I need!  A fathom core is an incredible well of information that we will be able to draw much good from.  Whatever the Twilight\'s Hammer is up to in there - and believe me when I say it is no good - my comrades and I will now uncover.$B$BYou\'ve done well here today; the Earthen Ring looks upon you warmly for assisting us. You\'ve also helped the Horde as a whole, and for that you should be proud.' WHERE entry = 26891;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = '<Gorthak sighs disappointedly.>$B$BIf only you\'d arrived an hour ago....$B$BThe diplomat suffered mortal wounds at the hands of an elf assassin.$B$BHow the enemy was able to infiltrate the camp undetected remains a mystery.' WHERE entry = 13870;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Good, good!$B$BThe fewer \'a dem elves runnin\' around, the better.' WHERE entry = 6503;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Good to see a new face around here!$B$BThe forest crawls with Horde, but my assignment requires that I keep this outpost safe. I could really use someone who might be up for a good fight.' WHERE entry = 26408;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Avana is alive?! I feared that she might be dead when we heard about the attack on Maestra\'s Post!$B$BAs you can see, we have our hands full with the Horde here as well.$B$BYou have given me the greatest gift by letting me know she is well. Any time that you wish to ride one of my nightsabers back to Maestra\'s Post, it is yours.' WHERE entry = 13646;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Thank you!$B$BNow it\'s time to deal with the Horde!' WHERE entry = 13849;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = '<Commander Grimfang\'s brow wrinkles as he reads the report.>$B$BThis is grim news, indeed.$B$BMay the spirits preserve them until we can fight our way to Splintertree....' WHERE entry = 13848;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Ah, hello again $N. I was just reading the waves of the sea, much like I always do. What brings you to the outpost?' WHERE entry = 6922;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Did you have any trouble getting to the Light of Elune at Lake Falathim?', OfferRewardText = 'With the concoction blessed by the Light of Elune, it should be ready for delivery to Astranaar.$B$BThere is no time to waste, $N!' WHERE entry = 13642;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Have you gathered the Bathran\'s Hair, $N?  The child\'s health grows weaker by the hour....', OfferRewardText = 'Ah, you have the hair! This is a good first step. There are other ingredients that we will need, but the hair of the fallen Ancient could well be the most important.$B$BI only hope that whatever the Forsaken are devising from the plant will not be turned into a weapon. We simply do not have the numbers to remove them right now, especially with Maestra\'s Post under attack!' WHERE entry = 26473;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Yes, $R?', OfferRewardText = 'These venison should make our soldiers\' spirits rise for the coming battles. Here\'s something for your troubles.' WHERE entry = 13920;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Well done $S, well done! I will continue to send forces to thin out the furbolg, but I can at least count on a different path that will be free of Alliance entanglements. The Horde conquest of Ashenvale is now in full swing!$B$BYou\'ve earned your pay this day, hero.  I salute you!' WHERE entry = 216;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Did Commander Grimfang send you? I\'ve asked him to find suitable recruits to aid me here.' WHERE entry = 26894;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Thank Elune you\'re here! We could use all the help we can get.' WHERE entry = 26897;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Thank Elune you\'re here! We could use all the help we can get.' WHERE entry = 26898;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Your deeds today shall live long in the Horde\'s glorious history.$B$BYour efforts have dealt a devastating blow to the enemy!' WHERE entry = 13947;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Tainting the Forest\'s Heart?$B$BHow ruthless - an utterly vicious blow....$B$BI adore the idea!' WHERE entry = 13803;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Well done, $R. But there is much that remains to be done here.' WHERE entry = 13943;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'You got those parts I need, friend?', OfferRewardText = 'This looks right, $C.$B$BI should have your shredder put together in no time.' WHERE entry = 13983;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'You say that Faldreas sent you? Good man.$B$BAs it happens, we could use your help.' WHERE entry = 13965;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'A fine job, my little $R friend. But as you can see, I am a little busy here.' WHERE entry = 13985;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'With their gates closed and no further reinforcements coming, it is only a matter of time now before the demons are no more.$B$BYou are a hero of the forest, $N. I give you thanks on behalf of all of Ashenvale\'s creatures!' WHERE entry = 13766;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = '<Thagg listens intently as you recount your assault on Astranaar.>$B$BThis is good news indeed, <race>. But right now, we need more than just good news here.$B$BThese triage kits will be put to good use!' WHERE entry = 13958;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'What\'s troubling you, $C?', OfferRewardText = 'A troll charm? What are the furbolg doing with such a thing?$B$BYou\'re right, it does have a feeling of corruption about it... even I can sense that.$B$BThere\'s someone here who might be able to help.' WHERE entry = 13868;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Gorka...$B$BWe must always be prepared for losses. Her honorable service to the Horde will not be forgotten.$B$BAnd her sacrifice shall not be in vain!' WHERE entry = 13653;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Well done, $N.$B$BWe are under constant threat from the furbolg. Hopefully this will keep them at bay for a bit longer.' WHERE entry = 13867;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Yes, yes... you appear as one of my kind, but I care not what you truly are if you can help the furbolg.$B$BThe night elves and now the orcs have visited many atrocities upon my people.$B$BCorruption runs through our veins, corruption brought down upon us by the prideful night elves and the warlike orcs. They are the ones who did this to our people... They are the ones I blame for being cast out of my tribe.$B$BAt night I can still see the campfires burning in the darkness.' WHERE entry = 26480;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Woohooo!!$B$BYou\'ve silenced the voices! Thank you, thank you!' WHERE entry = 13801;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Excellent!$B$BLet the naga retreat back into the seas where they belong!' WHERE entry = 13901;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'A brutal display, but one fitting for the enemies of Ashenvale. The Horde dares to think that they can take our beloved forest away from us.$B$BThey are fatally mistaken!$B$BYou have saved Raynewood from destruction, $N. Surely we can find a reward suitable for our champion?' WHERE entry = 13935;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'You\'re a brave one to come here given the circumstances.$B$BWhat business have you, stranger?', OfferRewardText = 'So, Evenar was succesful. Actually, more to the point, YOU were successful.$B$BI cannot thank you enough, $C, but there is more that must be done to the leaves before they will serve as a curative for what ails the child, Relara.' WHERE entry = 13623;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Good work, $R.$B$BOne less thing we have to worry about!' WHERE entry = 13806;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'You have my respect and thanks, $C Perhaps we\'ll be able to create a new home here without having to worry about the Burning Legion yet again.' WHERE entry = 26444;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'That\'s better!  There\'s nothing quite like ridding our world of a demon.  And they make for worthy opponents as well, unlike the weak races of the Alliance.' WHERE entry = 26448;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'What do you have there, sir?', OfferRewardText = 'By the Seven Crystals of Ata\'mal, this cannot be! They plan to attack Forest Song?!$B$BNot on my watch!$B$B<Vindicator Vedaar crumples the demon-scrawled plans in his fist.>$B$BNo. We will not allow this to happen!' WHERE entry = 26443;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'What do you have there, scout?', OfferRewardText = 'Dreadlords!  They plan to attack us here at Splintertree Post?!$B$BNot while I still draw breath!$B$B<Valusha crumples the demon-scrawled plans in her fist.>$B$BNo.  We will not allow this to happen!  They are a blight upon our world!' WHERE entry = 26447;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Have you collected the ore we need?', OfferRewardText = 'Well done! These should hold a curse long enough for our purposes....' WHERE entry = 13797;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = '<The sentinel eyes you appreciatively for a moment.>$B$BA job well done, $C. If you\'re any indication of the quality of the $R adventurers we\'re going to be seeing more of, we should have this war against the orcs and their Horde taken care of faster than expected.' WHERE entry = 13594;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Have you brought me the head of the enemy, $R?', OfferRewardText = 'Grah... very well.$B$BI\'ll remove the bounty I had placed upon your head. Though I am sorely tempted to end your life anyway, just on principle.$B$BBe sure that you never raise my ire again, $N. Now, get out of my sight...' WHERE entry = 13842;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Hello. How are you?', OfferRewardText = 'Oh, Raene sent you? It must be serious indeed.$B$BWhat can I help you with?' WHERE entry = 26476;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'You found my brother!  He was captured by the Thistlefurs?  That is terrible news to hear, for although many Furbolgs are noble creatures, the Thistlefurs are corrupt.$B$BThank you for rescuing my brother, $N. I do not want to think of how they treated poor Ruul. He will likely sleep long after this ordeal...' WHERE entry = 6482;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'My brother must have sent you. He wouldn\'t have done so unless you are capable of doing what must be done.$B$BFor all of our sakes I hope that he\'s right.$B$BThe elementals here are now my allies. You must do as they ask if we are to prevent the destruction of the rest of Ashenvale.' WHERE entry = 13877;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Well done, $R.$B$BThe elf captain is dead and the soul of one of our beloved brethren can sleep in peace.$B$BI shall pass on word of your deeds to my superiors in Orgrimmar.' WHERE entry = 13621;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = '$N, did you find the remains of the lake?  Do you have the Tear?', OfferRewardText = 'Oh, you found it! Odd... it looks tarnished somehow. I will place the tear in a stew, and pray that it will cure her.$B$BThank you! Thank you, $N!' WHERE entry = 26475;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Have you collected the arrows we need, $C?', OfferRewardText = 'Well done, $C.$B$BThis should help get us by until our shipment arrives.' WHERE entry = 13615;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'I saw those explosions all of the way from over here! Those filthy orcs and their goblin lackeys are going to have a hard time doing anything to despoil the forest now!$B$BWe can\'t thank you enough, $N. Will this do?' WHERE entry = 13698;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Did you find Gorat, $C?!', OfferRewardText = '<Kadrak listens intently as you share Gorat\'s last words.>$B$BIt is as I feared, then. May his rest be peaceful - only not yet!' WHERE entry = 13619;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Listen carefully, $R....' WHERE entry = 13618;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Teronis\' body lies broken atop the small rise next to the Keeper.$B$BDeep slashes crisscross his corpse.' WHERE entry = 26463;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'You found my brother!  He was captured by the Thistlefurs?  That is terrible news to hear, for although many Furbolgs are noble creatures, the Thistlefurs are corrupt.$B$BThank you for rescuing my brother, $N.  I do not want to think of how they treated poor Ruul. He will likely sleep long after this ordeal...' WHERE entry = 6482;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'My brother must have sent you. He wouldn\'t have done so unless you are capable of doing what must be done.$B$BFor all of our sakes I hope that he\'s right.$B$BThe elementals here are now my allies. You must do as they ask if we are to prevent the destruction of the rest of Ashenvale.' WHERE entry = 13877;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Well done, $R.$B$BThe elf captain is dead and the soul of one of our beloved brethren can sleep in peace.$B$BI shall pass on word of your deeds to my superiors in Orgrimmar.' WHERE entry = 13621;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Welcome, $C. It is good to see that the road to Mor\'shan Ramparts remains clear.' WHERE entry = 13628;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Hello, $N.', OfferRewardText = '<Recognizing at once the nature of the gift, Draaka begins to weep.>$B$BOh, $N. Thank you for this gift! It means more than you could know.$B$BHe hasn\'t forgotten...' WHERE entry = 13875;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = '<The satyr sneers, but when he realizes you are not here to chastise him, he changes his expression.>$B$BFinally, my redemption is at hand. I have waited long for this day and I think I know how to help you in turn.' WHERE entry = 13921;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Have you come to help us fight back against the forces of the Horde? Every blade and spell will be needed!' WHERE entry = 28492;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Done?', OfferRewardText = 'Well done, $R. Lord Magmathar\'s fire is now trapped, restrained within the earth once more.' WHERE entry = 13880;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'If we are to be free, we must have Kaliva\'s heart.', OfferRewardText = 'Disgusting, I know, but if we three are to be free of Kaliva\'s chains, it is not enough that she is dead.$B$BWe must eat of her fel heart!' WHERE entry = 13982;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Good. Murgut sold his own tribe out to the Horde, allying with them when they took your precious Silverwind Refuge in order to \'save\' his people.$B$BHe sold them into slavery, or worse. And now he has gotten what he deserved!$B$BLet us speak now of a different traitor, one whom I believe has something that will make that rod of yours even more powerful.' WHERE entry = 13989;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Were you able to recover that armor plating, $R?', OfferRewardText = 'Good work, $R.$B$BI\'ll show them how an armored ship should be built!' WHERE entry = 13883;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Nice work, $N.$B$BYou\'ve demoralized the enemy and harvested resources for the Horde.$B$BLet\'s hope the rest of the mission goes as well.' WHERE entry = 13815;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Did you get the wood you need?', OfferRewardText = 'It seems you\'ve solved one problem only to face another, $C. ' WHERE entry = 13640;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Whatcha got there, boss?', OfferRewardText = '<Jinx examines the powder carefully for a moment.>$B$BHmmm.$B$BIt\'ll take a little time. But yes, we can put this into a bomb....' WHERE entry = 13977;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Five moonstones are required to assure that the girl is healed.', OfferRewardText = 'You have all of the moonstones that are needed. And yet, it is said that a sacrifice of life is the only way to be ensure the saving of another.$B$BI will ensure that no matter what, the moonstones will cure Relara.' WHERE entry = 13922;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Rest in peace, my friends.$B$B<You can see the sorrow in the druid cat\'s eyes.>$B$BI felt the anguish of the Dor\'danil Barrows lessen, and knew that you had completed your task.$B$BIt was grim work that you did, $N, for the spirits you destroyed were merely victims of the Horde\'s evil. But with their destruction, let us hope the maddened spirits will finally find peace.' WHERE entry = 26472;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'This globe... it is most disturbing. Many of the more powerful elementals receive their power and energy through such devices.  To find one like this nearly intact is one thing - to find it so tainted is another.$B$BI will see that this globe is studied properly by the Earthen Ring.  Perhaps we can bring an end to this corruption of the elements. Please - accept this as a fair exchange for bringing this globe to the attention of the Earthen Ring.' WHERE entry = 824;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Nice work, $R!$B$BNo more ships will run aground, thanks to you.' WHERE entry = 13890;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Did you defeat Chief Murgut, $N?  Did you retrieve his Foulweald Totem?', OfferRewardText = 'Good work, $N. Issuing that challenge to the Foulwealds and defeating their leader sends them a strong message:$B$BThe Horde is not to be trifled with.$B$BI don\'t believe that tribe will be giving us much trouble for a long time.' WHERE entry = 6621;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'You have your work cut out for you here, friend.$B$BLet\'s hope that you\'re up to the task,,,,' WHERE entry = 13808;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Good work, $C!$B$BYour efforts will help keep the enemy on their heels while our forces sweep across the land!' WHERE entry = 13612;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'The naga increase in numbers, $N. Please complete this task for me.', OfferRewardText = 'We could use more of your kind around here, $N. Thank you for your help.' WHERE entry = 6442;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Very well done, $N. Your actions in the Zoram Strand against the naga are commendable.$B$BI know your feat was not easily accomplished, for the strength and guile of the naga is well known to the night elves. We know this, for we share a history with them.$B$BThe naga are cursed Highborne night elves. Ten thousand years ago, Queen Azshara made a pact of desperation with the Old Gods to save her surviving people from a watery grave.$B$BThe naga are the result of that pact.' WHERE entry = 13602;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Were you able to collect the oil we need, $C?', OfferRewardText = 'Thank you for the oil, $C. Now prepare yourself!$B$BMy runner has returned with some desperate news....$B$BSplintertree is surrounded!' WHERE entry = 13651;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Our night elf scouts report that preparations for the attack are almost complete. Those dreadlords must die soon, $N!', OfferRewardText = 'Never again will the Burning Legion threaten Ashenvale! You have delivered us from a fight we very likely would have lost, $C.$B$BI give you thanks, $N, and the deepest gratitude of the Hand of Argus. It honors me to have you at our side!' WHERE entry = 26445;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Those dreadlords must die soon, $N!', OfferRewardText = 'Never again will the Burning Legion make slaves of the orcs, or any other race of the Horde!$B$BBravely fought, $C!  You have the true heart of the Horde beating inside of you!  You give us much honor!' WHERE entry = 26449;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'You have helped me to return to the ground, $N.$B$BNow my hair will cease to sprout for these creatures. Better yet, I will be regrown all the sooner.' WHERE entry = 13595;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'I must apologize, for I have no time to speak. My child, Relara, is deathly ill!', OfferRewardText = 'This is from Orendil?$B$BHis skill with herbs and healing is great! This cure gives me hope, when before I had little....' WHERE entry = 26474;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'It is done?$B$BGood work, $N. That will gradually weaken their forces, as well as their spirit.' WHERE entry = 13805;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Did you find the final piece of the rod, <name>? How did my technique work?', OfferRewardText = 'You got it? Wonderful for you... and for Raene!$B$BI guess we\'ll have to see about reassembling it, won\'t we?' WHERE entry = 26478;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Oh, yes!$B$BThis will teach those elves, just you watch!' WHERE entry = 13730;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'You acquitted yourself well in battle on the field. However, I\'m afraid that Lord Magmathar has taken notice of you and the destruction that you\'ve wreaked upon his minions.$B$BYou will have to deal with him or he is sure to burn you alive, $N.' WHERE entry = 13884;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Did you feel it, $N!?$B$BThe raw fel power seething through your being?$B$BThere is nothing else like it!' WHERE entry = 13798;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'We are in your debt, $C If I know anything about the furbolg, they do not like their noses bloodied.$B$BIt won\'t be long now before they tuck tail and return to their village.' WHERE entry = 13632;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Good. Though it may take a great deal of your years for the seedlings to grow into ancients, in the fullness of time they will aid us in our fight against all of the enemies of Ashenvale.' WHERE entry = 26446;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'I\'m amazed that you broke through the Horde lines and managed to get in here, $R.', OfferRewardText = 'Thank you, $C. We have our hands full defending the retreat, but when I can catch my breath, I\'ll see to it that these sisters are returned to life, the goddess willing.$B$BYou\'ve demonstrated your prowess... we can use your help.' WHERE entry = 13928;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Have you the remains, little one?', OfferRewardText = 'I have lived a very long time in peace with the forest, but what these orc-things are doing makes me want to feed them back to the ground!$B$BI will put this wood to rest now. Thank you for this kindness, $N. I will never forget.' WHERE entry = 13869;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'What\'s that you have there, $C?', OfferRewardText = 'Thank you for delivering this report, <class>. From what Sentinel Melyria writes, it seems our worst fears have come to pass. With each advance we make, the Horde appears more determined to do as much damage as possible.$B$BWe can\'t afford to back down; the fate of our ancestral lands hangs in the balance. With more people like you on the frontlines, I\'m certain we could triumph.$B$BWill you join our fight? A new front has just opened in Warsong Gulch to the south.' WHERE entry = 26456;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Thank you, $R. I shall include your service to the Horde in my report.$B$BI should have these troops fit to fight again in no time!' WHERE entry = 13613;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Our losses here have been staggering.', OfferRewardText = 'I do not look forward to writing the letter to the Argent Dawn embassy in Darnassus. At least we\'ll be able to send their most prized possessions back for their loved ones.$B$BI cannot thank you enough for your courage, $N. Please accept this on behalf of the post.' WHERE entry = 13626;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Well done, $N! With the befouled elemental numbers thinned and Tideress put back into the lake, we should be able to launch a counter-offensive on Silverwind Refuge.$B$B$B$BJust as soon as we\'re done with defending the spire....' WHERE entry = 26470;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'We\'re saved! You\'ve shot down enough of them that we should be able to handle the rest.$B$BI cannot thank you enough, $N.' WHERE entry = 13853;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Yes, $N? How go your efforts?', OfferRewardText = 'You\'ve recreated the rod Teronis had set out to find? That\'s wonderful to hear.$B$BShael\'dryn has been indispensible in her assistance. Teronis would be proud to see his quest is continuing even after his tragic passing.$B$B<Raene looks over the reconstructed rod with a look of approval and thoughts racing behind her eyes.>$B$BNow it is time for us to make use of its power to eliminate the enemies of Ashenvale!' WHERE entry = 26479;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'It is said that the Ring of Zoram is the key to any lock within the city. Do you have it, $N?', OfferRewardText = 'You found the ring! Thank you, $N.$B$BPlease take this as payment, and know that your deeds today will remain forever in my memory.' WHERE entry = 26466;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'I hope you can be quick about getting those horns, $N. I\'m heading back to Ratchet soon!', OfferRewardText = 'These are perfect, $N! Thanks for helping me out!$B$BOh, and this is for your time...' WHERE entry = 6441;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Please, help me avenge Anilia\'s death.', OfferRewardText = 'Thank you, kind $R. My sister\'s spirit is gladdened by your efforts.' WHERE entry = 26469;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'It upsets me so that the treants have become corrupt. I wish I could do more to help them.', OfferRewardText = 'I\'m pleased to see you\'re back, $N.' WHERE entry = 26477;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'I want to know one thing, $R.$B$BIs that assassin dead?', OfferRewardText = 'Well done, $C.%B$BOne last request - it would probably be best if none of my laborers knew this assassin ever existed.' WHERE entry = 13871;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Let\'s see what you\'ve brought me, $R.', OfferRewardText = 'This is PERFECT!$B$BOh, just wait \'til you see what I can do with this....' WHERE entry = 13942;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Yes, $C?', OfferRewardText = 'Shadumbra\'s Head?$B$BNone can say how many of our Horde brethren have fallen to this beast over the years. Your prowess has ensured that no more shall suffer this fate.$B$BWarchief Hellscream shall hear of your deeds, $C.' WHERE entry = 24;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'What have you there, $C? Could it be....?', OfferRewardText = 'You have slain the beast?$B$BI owe you a great debt, friend. That beast terrorized many over the years, but its death holds special meaning to me.$B$BYou see, recently my brother fell victim to these very claws... I shall sleep well now, knowing that he has been avenged.' WHERE entry = 2;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = '<Gurtar listens as you inform him of Sheelah\'s passing.>$B$BI\'ll deliver this to Hellscream personally, $R.$B$BIn the meantime, there\'s something I need you to do for me....' WHERE entry = 13873;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Well done, $C.$B$BA fitting end to a textbook assault.' WHERE entry = 25;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'So, Tweedle found a way to get those explosives working, eh?$B$BIt\'s about time...' WHERE entry = 13944;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Very well, $N.$B$BYou have succeeded where I could not. You have earned my respect.' WHERE entry = 13962;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'We are in your debt, $C.$B$BUnable to complete their nefarious rituals, the satyr are now fighting a losing battle where they are unable to replenish their numbers.' WHERE entry = 13683;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'What\'s this? Who are you!?$B$B<Durak reads Draaka\'s note.>$B$BHrmphh...$B$BDraaka should know better than to be so brazen, but it looks like you\'re up to your eyes in this with as much to lose as anyone.$B$BVery well.' WHERE entry = 13751;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'With the death of the harbinger, I can begin to cleanse the lake.$B$BYou have my deepest thanks, $N. I mourn the loss of your friend, but know that his remains will fuel the reclamation of the forest hereabouts.' WHERE entry = 13644;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Have you found many statuettes, $N?', OfferRewardText = 'That\'s quite a few that you have found! Thank you, $N!$B$BThe old city of Zoram holds many secrets, and these statuettes may be the key to many of them.' WHERE entry = 26465;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Yeah, what do you need?', OfferRewardText = 'You find a nasty ball of water and decide to bring it to me?  Who am I, the Earthen Ring or something?$B$BActually, that does give me an idea... perhaps you do need the Earthen Ring for this.  I mean, if it helps clear up the situation at the lake for good, then I\'m all for it.$B$BYou know who the Earthen Ring are, $N?' WHERE entry = 1918;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Have you found them? What did Anilia say? Where is she?', OfferRewardText = 'Anilia died? No... that can\'t be! It was just yesterday that we were running and playing together in the woods.$B$BI guess those days are over...' WHERE entry = 26468;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'How goes your search for the crystals, $N? Do you think they\'ll make an item we can use to stop the naga?', OfferRewardText = 'Excellent! These will do nicely. Here\'s a reward for your hard work.' WHERE entry = 26890;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = '$N, you have returned.', OfferRewardText = 'The Forest Heart! It\'s corrupted!$B$B<The great ancient creaks as its immense limbs begin to perform a ritual.>$B$BStand back, $N, I will try to cleanse the heart before all is lost!' WHERE entry = 13796;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Did you shut that disgusting, wart-ridden goblin up for good?', OfferRewardText = 'That\'s better. Without him, their technicians are sure to fall back to their normal laziness, which should result in fewer bombs and more accidents.' WHERE entry = 13979;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'You\'ve saved us all, $N! I have the power to finish off these final few.$B$BNo longer will the forest have to fear the Burning Legion!' WHERE entry = 13987;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Can you feel it, $N, the touch of corruption upon the wind? If we do nothing, it will continue to advance. That is why I seek the Chalice of Elune. Were you able to find it?', OfferRewardText = 'Excellent work, $N. There is certainly a latent power here, one that not even constant exposure to the corruption of the satyr can dim.$B$BDo you see how it still shines, after all these years?' WHERE entry = 26455;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Ah, welcome back, $N.', OfferRewardText = 'This is terrible, $N. Teronis is dead?!$B$BThe time for mourning will come, but for now we must focus our efforts. I will send some of the Sentinels to recover Teronis\' body and to assist the keeper.$B$BYou have the gem that Teronis was seeking? It must be delivered to Astranaar.' WHERE entry = 26464;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Thank you, $N.$B$BWith the moonstones of Ordil\'Aran deactivated, we should not need to worry about any further incursions of furbolg here.$B$BHowever, my scouts have returned with disturbing news from the furbolg village. There is an imminent danger massing there.$B$BI wonder, might I entice you to carry a warning to Astranaar for me?' WHERE entry = 13630;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'You are brave to come here, $C, but you may be too late. All of the druids are either dead or have been driven insane.$B$BStill, your tale is intriguing, and if what you say is true, then Gnarl must have the Forest Heart and soon, or Ashenvale will begin to wither!' WHERE entry = 13792;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'They what? IT\'S HOW BIG?!!!$B$BI have a very bad feeling about this, $N.' WHERE entry = 13981;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Thank you, $N. Grim news you bring of the rest of the gnome team, but at least you managed to save a few. For that I am grateful.' WHERE entry = 13913;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Nice work, friend.$B$BYour skills have bought us the time we needed to prepare the bomb. It\'s almost complete!' WHERE entry = 13980;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Well, $N.$B$BIs it done?', OfferRewardText = 'Good work, $R.$B$BThis should keep them licking their wounds for a time.' WHERE entry = 13967;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = '$C, you must be wary! Kaliva, the foul demoness who has chained us is nearby!' WHERE entry = 13976;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = '<The goblin stares at you and blinks several times before speaking.>$B$BThe spirits whispered that help would soon arrive.$B$BPardon my surprise, but I was hoping the spirits would guide someone a little more... heroic.$B$BThese elementals are trusted allies. Listen to them and do their bidding. If we fail, there will remain nothing in Ashenvale worth fighting for.' WHERE entry = 13879;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'What have you there, $R?', OfferRewardText = 'Let\'s have a look, $C.' WHERE entry = 13620;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'You come here as a child, $R.$B$BYou shall leave here a battle-hardened $C of the Horde!$B$BThat, or a corpse....' WHERE entry = 13923;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'I am Raene Wolfrunner. Who might you be?', OfferRewardText = 'Teronis is dead?$B$B<The lady weeps softly for the loss of her friend and then composes herself after a moment.>$B$BWe must see to it that his sacrifice was not in vain. Are you willing to see this through, $C?$B$BVery well, allow me some time to think about how we should proceed. I will know shortly.' WHERE entry = 13645;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'You\'re the reinforcements that Thork sent?$B$BYou\'ll do fine as long you can kill night elves. The forest is crawling with them.' WHERE entry = 28876;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'You are just in time, $C. Old Kulg has been slinking around those woods too long. He grows too cautious, jumping at shadows. We will fear this forest no longer - the time has come to subdue Ashenvale once and for all!' WHERE entry = 13866;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Gorka\'s death was not in vain, $N.$B$BSplintertree would have certainly fallen if we hadn\'t come when we did.$B$BNow we must get to work shoring up her defenses.$B$BThis isn\'t over....' WHERE entry = 13712;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Good to finally meet you, $N. I\'ve heard all about what you\'ve been up to and let me just say that I\'m impressed!$B$BThink you can lend us your expertise?' WHERE entry = 13964;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Well? The future of the Thistlefur rests upon your shoulders, $R.', OfferRewardText = 'What was done had to be done. As our leader, Dal\'s sickness from the troll charms was destroying us.$B$BIt was better for the health and dignity of the tribe that it was you, outsider. This way there will be no civil war amongst us and we will easily find new leadership... hopefully one that does not have a tendency to so easily trust outsiders. Perhaps I am guilty of this as well?$B$BHere, allow me to repay the debt we owe you before we part ways forever.' WHERE entry = 13876;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'So Torek\'s attack was successful! Well done, $N. Night elves are decent foes. A little skinny, but strong and fierce! I\'m sure the battle was something to see...$B$BAnd I hope you gained a scar or two!' WHERE entry = 6544;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Did you find the charms, $N? Every moment the furbolgs possess those sacred items, my blood boils with rage!', OfferRewardText = 'You found them! Thank you! Thank you, $N! You do not know how great a thing you have done for me.$B$BA troll without his charm is like an orc without his battle scars...$B$BWorthless. ' WHERE entry = 6462;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'You return, $N. What\'s that affixed to the top of the rod? A skull?', OfferRewardText = 'So, you used the skull of the furbolg king to modify the power of Dartol\'s Rod? You then used that power to convince the captured furbolg to rise up and attack the Horde at Silverwind Refuge?$B$BI am more than pleased and impressed with your abilities, $N. The Sentinels cannot thank you enough. It should be a simple matter for us to sweep away the orcs and retake the refuge now!$B$BTeronis would be proud. You have my deepest respect.' WHERE entry = 26482;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Let me tell ya somethin\' $C!$B$BThe bossman simply doesn\'t appreciate the art and craftsmanship that goes into making fine explosives.' WHERE entry = 13936;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Well, look at this! Little Tweedle has really come through this time. This stuff blew up Astranaar, you say?$B$BAs you can see, we don\'t need any help taking over Silverwind Refuge, but Tweedle\'s ideas are as small as his hands.$B$BIf this stuff\'s really as good as you say, there\'s no limit to what we might do....' WHERE entry = 13974;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'What is it, $R?', OfferRewardText = 'The paw of Ursangous!$B$BHave you any idea what trouble this beast has caused us over the years? Those days are over now, thanks to you.$B$BI shall forward this trophy on to Orgrimmar to be put on display, along with your account of its death.$B$BCongratulations!' WHERE entry = 23;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Judging by the gaping wound in her side, Anilia is on the verge of death.' WHERE entry = 26467;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'I have witnessed many naga attacks since I arrived here. It puts my mind at ease that Vorsha will no longer roam freely.$B$BWe are in your debt, $N.' WHERE entry = 6641;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'It is done. The power of fire is subdued and the four elements are returned to harmony.$B$BYou have saved the rest of Ashenvale through your brave and selfless actions, $N. You have our eternal thanks.' WHERE entry = 13886;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'You\'ve done it! The spirits were right after all!$B$BThe power of fire is subdued and the four elements are returned to harmony.$B$BThe rest of Ashenvale is spared this fiery fate. You have the eternal thanks of the Earthen Ring.' WHERE entry = 13888;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'So you\'re the reinforcements? I suppose you\'ll do fine as long you can kill night elves.' WHERE entry = 28493;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Take my update to Kadrak. Swiftly, $N.' WHERE entry = 6546;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Let Kadrak know of the success we have had here holding off the night elves. Our plans are going well.' WHERE entry = 6547;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Hello, $C.$B$BWhat\'s that? You say that Shyela sent you?$B$B$B$BVery well, let\'s get started.' WHERE entry = 13617;
UPDATE quest_template SET OfferRewardText = 'Well done, $C.$B$BThey\'re in complete disarray. Just look at them!' WHERE entry = 13865;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = '<The worgen gives you a blank look as you walk up to him.>', OfferRewardText = '<Looking down at the wooden carving in your extended hand, the worgen reaches out to take it.>' WHERE entry = 13872;
UPDATE quest_template SET RequestItemsText = 'Ze junk? Do you have zit?', OfferRewardText = 'Ah, ze junk haz arrived! Zit is ze last piece of ze puzzle! Now to zet it up! Standby, $N!' WHERE entry = 25607;  